snippet.textDisplay:
Hello! For the ones in the want, here's the translation of what he's saying. An Irish friend translated this for me and he allowed me to share it with the world.
"""
Top of the mornin!
I'm Irish - Irish the Hedgehod!

I was going to meet up with me old friends Tilly and Sonk when suddenly, I thought, "You know I've a mouth on me for some good ol' praties..."

And so then I went down towards Station Square and I bump into Big and it's just like, "How's the Big size a ye?" and he's all like, "Irish! How in the name of Tikal are ye?"

And I'm just all "Story horse how's it going? What's the craic? [all different ways of saying "How are you doing"]"
and then he's like "Sonk was just here but that eejit was natterin' about nothin'." [Best way to say it internationally would be "That fool was talking nonsense" or "talking shite"]

And so then I thought of me aul fella [my father], and suddenly Big says "Get outta that Garden!" [No way!] -
and I thought he might've gone stone mad and maybe he's just sick as a box of frogs [very sick]

But then I'm thinking well with Big he's a few short of a full shilling [Not all there in the head] and quite frankly his mouth is the size of an aul lads (skin? not sure this one myself) [the meaning behind it either way is that he has a big mouth, not literally, but he talks big] and some say he's the owner of the giant's causeway [the sun shines out of his arse]
"""
Praise the Irish!
And Irish the hedgehog: Welcome to the roster! I hope you can find some spot for ya

snippet.textDisplay:
Some of my Headcanons for this guy:

Just as seen in this video, Irish tends to speak in an incredibly strong Irish accent, and only those who've been his friends for years (Big, Sonic, Tails, etc) can best understand him.

Irish isn't limited to just one weapon, his clover can turn to anything to suit his needs; a hammer, a sword, a grapple, or even a laser gun, if you think it, his clover can turn into it.

Is one of the loudest of Sonic's friends, and isn't afraid to let himself be heard, which Rouge figured out the hard way (after stopping her from stealing a Chaos Emerald, Irish let her HAVE it).

He always itches for an unfair fight, wanting that pump of adrenaline. Doesn't matter if the odds are a million to one, he somehow manages to win.

Is one of the luckiest members of Team Sonic. Due to this, he gets the most Rings out of everyone, and it definitely has its perks.
